Also known as: Loss:Time:Life (Original Story)
Synopsis:
If there is something you could do right before you die, what would you do? This drama is a Korean remake of the popular Japanese romance drama “Loss:Time:Life”.
So Jin (Mina) is a young high school teacher who is about to die. However, she is granted the chance to live 30 more hours after her death. She will find the true meaning of life and love through the 30 hours.
